rationale: Amendment A-7 mandates this snapshot. The required color-preserving Manifold render, 3MF color export, and 3MF export options exist only in the snapshot line, and 2026.06.12 is the first cross-platform snapshot after upstream PR #6857 fixed multi-mesh 3MF color export against lib3mf 1.x. Earlier snapshots may carry that defect; stable 2021.01 lacks the required color and multi-object 3MF capabilities.
